Grandma cut the prone juice!

467
00:45:56.968 --> 00:45:59.891
What level are you on?
- Sixth...

468
00:46:09.064 --> 00:46:13.096
Don't you want to
see something classified?

469
00:46:18.640 --> 00:46:21.462
I need a moment... please.
- Sorry.

470
00:46:22.772 --> 00:46:24.284
And save my game.

471
00:46:24.285 --> 00:46:26.502
How classified?

472
00:46:27.610 --> 00:46:31.844
Like. I-will-go-to-jail-for-the-rest-
-of-my-life-for-showing-you classified.

473
00:46:32.953 --> 00:46:34.364
One quick peak.

474
00:46:34.767 --> 00:46:37.791
Spec Ops got a thermal snapshot
of whatever hit the base in Qatar.

475
00:46:37.792 --> 00:46:40.613
I wanna see it.
- The imager was damaged sir.

476
00:46:40.614 --> 00:46:44.242
The rangers are in rout with
the imager. but we also have a security issue.

477
00:46:44.243 --> 00:46:46.963
Server logs indicate one of the
analysts made a copy of the network

478
00:46:46.964 --> 00:46:48.778
intrusion signal.

479
00:46:51.902 --> 00:46:54.624
The signal strength is through the roof.
where did you said you got this?

480
00:46:54.625 --> 00:46:58.656
Hacked the national military
air guard frequency in less than a minute.

481
00:46:58.657 --> 00:47:00.571
No way...

482
00:47:02.486 --> 00:47:04.804
Looks like there's a message
embedded in the signal.

483
00:47:05.207 --> 00:47:07.425
Gotta be worth my magic.

484
00:47:13.271 --> 00:47:15.892
Project "Iceman"?
- What's Sector 7?

485
00:47:16.396 --> 00:47:18.714
