486
00:47:18.715 --> 00:47:21.234
Are you playing those
videogames again?

487
00:47:22.242 --> 00:47:24.359
Cops!

488
00:47:39.680 --> 00:47:43.208
Get off my grandma's carpet!
She don't like nobody on her carpet!

489
00:47:43.209 --> 00:47:45.526
Especially police!

490
00:47:45.527 --> 00:47:52.179
<i>It was an awesome spectacle here an hour
