493
00:48:09.213 --> 00:48:12.136
Miles listen to me.
My car. it stole itself ok?

494
00:48:12.237 --> 00:48:15.664
What are you talking about man?
- Satan's Camaro in my yard.

495
00:48:15.665 --> 00:48:17.579
It is stalking me.

496
00:48:35.723 --> 00:48:37.537
Sam?

497
00:48:40.964 --> 00:48:43.887
That was really...
Awesome.

498
00:48:44.895 --> 00:48:46.709
It felt awesome.
- Are you ok?

499
