500
00:48:48.424 --> 00:48:51.044
Getting chased by my car
right now. I gotta go.

501
00:48:51.044 --> 00:48:53.463
You know what. I'm gonna
go. I'll check with you guys later.

502
00:49:26.121 --> 00:49:27.935
Great. the cops.

503
