Officer!

504
00:49:34.890 --> 00:49:36.200
Listen...

505
00:49:38.720 --> 00:49:40.434
That hurt.

506
00:49:42.853 --> 00:49:45.373
Listen to me.
Thank God you're here.

507
00:49:45.574 --> 00:49:49.606
I've had the worst day ever.
I've been followed here on my mother's bike.

508
00:49:50.413 --> 00:49:52.933
And my car is right there
and it has been following me here.

509
00:49:52.934 --> 00:49:54.848
So get out of the car.

510
00:50:13.797 --> 00:50:16.217
Please. what do you want from me?!

511
00:50:38.190 --> 00:50:39.803
This is a bad dream.

512
00:50:41.416 --> 00:50:44.843
Are you username LadiesMan217?
- I don't know what you're talking about!

513
00:50:44.844 --> 00:50:48.270
Are you username LadiesMan217?!
- Yeah...

514
00:50:48.271 --> 00:50:52.302
Where is the eBay item 21153?!
Where are the glasses?!

515
00:51:03.893 --> 00:51:05.909
Get back!

516
00:51:12.461 --> 00:51:15.686
What is your problem Sam?!
- There's a monster right there. it just attacked me!

517
00:51:16.190 --> 00:51:18.105
Here it comes!

518
00:51:28.286 --> 00:51:30.100
Sam what is that thing?
- You have to get in the car.

519
00:51:30.101 --> 00:51:33.124
Get in the car.
Trust me!

520
00:51:54.997 --> 00:51:56.912
We're gonna die!
- We're not gonna die!

521
00:52:29.066 --> 00:52:30.880
We're locked in.

522
