527
00:55:12.255 --> 00:55:14.070
It's a robot.

528
00:55:15.178 --> 00:55:19.613
Like a... different...
super advanced robot.

529
00:55:21.529 --> 00:55:23.645
He's probably Japanese.

530
00:55:23.646 --> 00:55:25.661
He's definitely Japanese.

531
00:55:26.972 --> 00:55:28.987
What are you doing?

532
00:55:29.391 --> 00:55:31.709
I don't think he wants to hurt us.
He would have done that already.

533
00:55:32.515 --> 00:55:37.656
Really? Well do you speak robot. because
they just had a giant twin death match.

534
00:55:39.873 --> 00:55:42.696
I think he wants something from me.
- What?

535
00:55:42.697 --> 00:55:45.518
Because the other one was
talking about my eBay page.

536
00:55:46.324 --> 00:55:49.348
You're the strangest
boy I have ever met.

537
00:55:49.752 --> 00:55:51.868
Can you talk?

538
00:55:55.396 --> 00:55:57.714
So you talk through the radio?

539
00:56:00.537 --> 00:56:02.553
So what was that last night?
What was that?

540
00:56:08.500 --> 00:56:10.717
"Visitors from heaven"...
What?

541
00:56:10.718 --> 00:56:13.136
Are you like an alien or something?

542
00:56:18.680 --> 00:56:20.898
Any more questions
you want to ask?

543
00:56:21.502 --> 00:56:23.619
He wants us to get in the car.

544
00:56:24.929 --> 00:56:26.945
And go where?

545
00:57:01.922 --> 00:57:03.736
This car is a pretty
good driver.

546
00:57:07.566 --> 00:57:09.481
Why don't you go sit
in that seat there?

547
