does he transform back into
this piece of crap Camaro?

556
00:58:05.020 --> 00:58:08.145
Fantastic!
Now you've pissed him off!

557
00:58:08.649 --> 00:58:11.774
That car is sensitive.
4000$ just drove off.

558
00:58:22.861 --> 00:58:24.675
What?

559
00:59:53.477 --> 00:59:55.795
This is easily a hundred times
cooler than Armageddon.

560
00:59:55.796 --> 00:59:57.912
I swear the God.

561
