564
01:01:11.897 --> 01:01:13.912
Holy cow what happened
to the pool?

565
01:02:47.451 --> 01:02:51.685
Are you Samuel James Witwicky
descendant of Archibald Witwicky?

566
01:02:52.995 --> 01:02:56.624
He knew your name.
- Yeah...

567
01:02:56.625 --> 01:02:59.144
My name is Optimus Prime.

568
01:02:59.145 --> 01:03:03.075
We are autonomous robotic organisms
from the planet Cybertron.

569
01:03:03.176 --> 01:03:05.796
But you can call us Autobots for short.

570
01:03:05.797 --> 01:03:07.208
Autobots?

571
01:03:07.209 --> 01:03:10.131
What's crackin' little bitches?
- My first lieutenant...

572
01:03:11.139 --> 01:03:14.364
Jazz... - This looks like a
cool place to kick it.

573
01:03:16.380 --> 01:03:18.497
