My weapons specialist. Ironhide.

576
01:03:27.064 --> 01:03:30.693
You feeling lucky punk?
- Easy Ironhide.

577
01:03:30.694 --> 01:03:33.515
Just kidding. I just wanted
to show him my talents.

578
01:03:35.128 --> 01:03:37.446
Our medical officer Ratchet.

579
01:03:37.447 --> 01:03:41.378
The boy's pheromone levels suggest
he wants to mate with the female.

580
01:03:43.897 --> 01:03:46.619
You already know your
guardian Bumblebee.

581
01:03:50.953 --> 01:03:52.868
You're my guardian?

582
01:03:53.473 --> 01:03:58.714
His vocal processor was damaged in battle.
We've been still working on him.

583
01:04:03.351 --> 01:04:07.081
Why are you here?
- We are here looking for the Allspark.

584
01:04:07.383 --> 01:04:10.004
And we must find it
before Megatron.

585
01:04:10.508 --> 01:04:12.120
Mega what?

586
