Our planet was once
a powerful empire.

587
01:04:25.526 --> 01:04:27.542
Peaceful and just.

588
01:04:28.349 --> 01:04:33.288
Until we were betrayed by Megatron.
leader of the Decepticons.

589
01:04:34.094 --> 01:04:36.815
All that were to fight
them were destroyed.

590
01:04:37.622 --> 01:04:44.073
Our war finally consumed the planet
and the Allspark was lost to the stars.

591
01:04:44.879 --> 01:04:47.701
Megatron followed it to Earth.

592
01:04:48.306 --> 01:04:50.423
When captain Witwicky found him.

593
01:04:51.935 --> 01:04:53.447
My grandfather...

594
01:04:53.448 --> 01:04:57.781
It was an accident that
intertwined our fates.

595
01:05:01.107 --> 01:05:03.023
Come back!

596
01:05:05.341 --> 01:05:07.558
The dogs have found something.

597
01:05:08.869 --> 01:05:11.187
The ice is cracking.

598
01:05:23.887 --> 01:05:25.702
I'm alright lads!

599
01:05:37.192 --> 01:05:41.728
Megatron crash-landed before
he could retrieve The Cube.

600
01:05:45.861 --> 01:05:48.885
Men. we've made a discovery!

601
01:05:49.187 --> 01:05:52.917
He accidentally activated
his navigation system.

602
01:06:07.331 --> 01:06:10.052
The coordinates to The Cube's
location on Earth

603
