604
01:06:13.077 --> 01:06:15.193
How did you know
about his glasses?

605
01:06:15.194 --> 01:06:17.309
eBay...

606
01:06:17.612 --> 01:06:20.736
If the Decepticons find the Allspark...

607
01:06:20.737 --> 01:06:24.466
They will use it's power to
transform Earth's machines

608
01:06:24.467 --> 01:06:29.607
and build a new army.
- And the human race will be extinguished.

609
01:06:30.413 --> 01:06:35.352
Sam Witwicky. you hold
the key to Earth's survival.

610
01:06:38.981 --> 01:06:41.299
Please tell me that
you have those glasses.

611
01:06:45.835 --> 01:06:48.959
It's like a self regenerating
molecular armor.

612
01:06:49.060 --> 01:06:51.379
Look at the scorch mark
where the Sable round hit.

613
01:06:51.380 --> 01:06:52.991
Melted right through.

614
01:06:52.992 --> 01:06:56.217
Aren't Sables hot loaded for
like a 6000 degree magnesium burn?

615
01:06:56.218 --> 01:06:58.334
Close to it. that was tank armor.

616
01:06:58.335 --> 01:07:00.652
This metal skin must
