Strap it down!
Strap it!

619
01:07:09.119 --> 01:07:10.933
This thing is wicked!

620
01:07:10.934 --> 01:07:13.251
Get on a hornet northern command.
tell them that our effective weapon

621
01:07:13.252 --> 01:07:16.276
is high heat Sable rounds.
Recommend we load them on all gunships. go.

622
01:07:21.214 --> 01:07:24.137
You want that peace?
Ok Maggie look.

623
01:07:26.456 --> 01:07:28.472
They're gonna come through
that door. play good cop bad cop.

624
01:07:28.473 --> 01:07:30.488
Don't fall for that. alright?

625
01:07:30.689 --> 01:07:32.100
That's why I ate their food.

626
01:07:32.101 --> 01:07:34.318
They put the plate of donuts
here to test your guilt.

627
01:07:34.822 --> 01:07:36.838
If you don't touch it you're guilty.

628
01:07:37.241 --> 01:07:40.063
I ate the whole plate.
The whole plate.

629
