It's me and you. They walk
through that door. you don't say nothing.

630
01:07:59.517 --> 01:08:02.238
She did it! She did it!
She's the one you want!

631
01:08:02.239 --> 01:08:05.363
I was just sitting home watching
cartoons. playing videogames with my cousin

632
01:08:05.364 --> 01:08:07.681
and she came in there. alright?
- Glenn you freak!

633
01:08:07.682 --> 01:08:09.597
I am not going to jail
for you or anybody else.

634
01:08:09.598 --> 01:08:12.116
I have done nothing bad
my entire life.

635
01:08:13.024 --> 01:08:14.939
Hey man. I'm still a virgin.

636
01:08:14.940 --> 01:08:17.660
So what. I’ve downloaded a
couple of thousand songs off the internet

637
01:08:17.661 --> 01:08:19.676
who hasn't?!

638
01:08:19.677 --> 01:08:21.894
Glenn shut up!
- No. you shut up!

639
01:08:21.895 --> 01:08:24.414
Don't talk to me!
Don't talk to me criminal!

640
01:08:27.135 --> 01:08:28.949
Sugar rush.
- This is not his fault.

641
01:08:29.453 --> 01:08:31.167
Can I go home now?

642
