Well I think it's a plane.

651
01:09:05.639 --> 01:09:07.958
Call Sam. he should be
home in 15 minutes.

652
01:09:07.959 --> 01:09:10.881
Well I'll call him in 15 minutes.
- If you wait 15 minutes he'll be late

653
