and you'll have to ground him.
- I can't ground him if he's not late. can I?

654
01:09:19.045 --> 01:09:21.767
Just stay here. alright?
You have to stay here and watch them.

655
01:09:22.170 --> 01:09:24.387
You hear what I'm saying?
5 minutes. alright?

656
01:09:25.395 --> 01:09:27.512
Thanks for staying on my path.

657
