Life is great.
- Life is fantastic. that's how good it is.

662
01:09:43.740 --> 01:09:45.857
The trash can. sorry dad.
I'm gonna do the trash cans. alright?

663
01:09:45.858 --> 01:09:47.369
No. I don't want you
to strain yourself.

664
01:09:48.276 --> 01:09:49.990
Dad. you'll hurt my feelings
if you do it.

665
01:09:49.991 --> 01:09:52.711
I promise... No. no. I'm gonna do it.

666
01:09:52.712 --> 01:09:56.340
I'm gonna do the trash cans and I'm gonna
