667
01:09:56.541 --> 01:09:59.061
Sweep up the whole house
right now.

668
01:09:59.062 --> 01:10:02.690
Right now?
- Right now.

669
01:10:04.101 --> 01:10:06.621
I love you.
God I love you.

670
01:10:07.226 --> 01:10:10.250
Just so much right now.
- You know. your mom wanted me to ground you.

671
01:10:10.251 --> 01:10:12.065
You're 3 minutes late.

672
01:10:12.266 --> 01:10:15.491
Just another thing you did for me
dad. because you're such a swell guy.

673
01:10:16.197 --> 01:10:19.221
Alright. I love you.
Sleep good handsome man.

674
01:10:20.531 --> 01:10:22.043
What are you doing?

675
01:10:22.044 --> 01:10:23.756
Watch the path!

676
01:10:27.990 --> 01:10:30.006
Sorry. my bad.

677
