You didn't even ground him.
- Almost. almost.

695
01:12:00.622 --> 01:12:02.940
Time is short.
- They really want those glasses.

696
01:12:06.165 --> 01:12:08.282
Please hurry.

697
01:12:09.996 --> 01:12:11.911
No. no. it's definitely gone.
- What do you mean?

698
01:12:11.912 --> 01:12:14.733
Glasses were in the bag. they were
in the backpack. now the backpack isn't here.

699
01:12:14.734 --> 01:12:16.547
Well they're gonna be
pissed. so what do you want to do?

700
01:12:16.548 --> 01:12:18.967
What I think you should do.
you should check this whole

701
01:12:18.968 --> 01:12:21.083
this whole section here.
Give it a clean sweep.

702
01:12:21.084 --> 01:12:22.797
And I'll get the corner here.

703
01:12:23.200 --> 01:12:26.022
Not there. that's my private.
Sorry.

704
01:12:26.526 --> 01:12:29.752
You just told me... - I didn't mean to
look inside of my treasure chest.

705
01:12:29.753 --> 01:12:31.365
You should be way more specific...

706
01:12:42.150 --> 01:12:43.964
This isn't hiding.
This isn't hiding.

707
01:12:43.965 --> 01:12:45.778
This is my back yard.
not a truck stop.

708
01:12:47.593 --> 01:12:50.717
<i>I saw it. UFO landed
right here and now is gone.</i>

709
01:12:51.322 --> 01:12:53.943
<i>My moped is under there
man. who's gonna pay for that?</i>

710
01:12:56.463 --> 01:12:58.781
Sam he's back.
Ok I'll deal with this.

711
01:12:59.890 --> 01:13:02.712
What?! No. no. no
these are my mother's flowers.

712
01:13:03.015 --> 01:13:05.031
Listen. you gotta listen to me.
If my parents come out here

713
01:13:05.032 --> 01:13:07.349
and they see you. they're gonna
freak out. My mom's got a temper.

714
01:13:07.853 --> 01:13:10.574
We must have the glasses.
- I know you need the glasses.

715
01:13:10.575 --> 01:13:13.296
I've been looking everywhere.
they're not here. they're definitely not here.

716
01:13:13.800 --> 01:13:16.924
Keep searching.
- I need you to be quiet for 5 minutes.

717
01:13:17.932 --> 01:13:20.856
Please. I'm begging you.
I can't concentrate.

718
01:13:20.857 --> 01:13:22.972
You want me to look...
- Calm down.

719
01:13:22.973 --> 01:13:24.787
You gotta do something.

720
01:13:24.788 --> 01:13:27.508
Autobots. fall back.
- Please for 5 minutes.

721
01:13:29.423 --> 01:13:32.649
Move! - What's the matter
with you. can't you be quiet?

722
01:13:32.650 --> 01:13:34.463
He wants us to be quiet...

723
01:13:38.596 --> 01:13:41.418
Earthquake! Move. move.
move. earthquake!

724
01:13:42.124 --> 01:13:45.147
Judy get under the table.
move it!

725
01:13:45.248 --> 01:13:47.970
Duck and cover right now!
- How did you get over there so fast?

726
01:13:49.179 --> 01:13:51.498
That was tingling.

727
01:13:51.800 --> 01:13:53.715
Yeah. that looks fun.
